extends layout

block content
  div(class="container-fluid")
    h1(class="header")
      | FreeCodeCamp API: Image Search Abstraction Layer
    blockquote
      p User stories:
      ol
        li I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
        li I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
        li I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.

    h3 Example query usage:
    blockquote
        p <a href="https://rafael-lin-image-search.herokuapp.com/lolcats%20funny?offset=10">https://rafael-lin-image-search.herokuapp.com/lolcats%20funny?offset=10</a>

